2023 October October, my birthday month рҹҺү is over and it&rsquo;s time to recap what I&rsquo;ve been doing!
Monthly principle &ldquo;Never start a chat with &lsquo;Hi&rsquo;.&rdquo; &ldquo;Reduce use of this and that, be clear and consise.&rdquo; &ldquo;Include full context in chat/email messages.&rdquo;
This months principles is about making communication more effective. As a friend of me wrote on hos blog timharek.no/blog/no-hello, starting a chat with &ldquo;Hi&rdquo; and then waiting for an answer, is a waste of time.
